    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >度假时一个小小的错误，可能引发大麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好面对那只踏上复仇之路的海狸了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't Mess With Bober —— 一款带有80年代恐怖电影风格的第一人称游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177010/extras/15d6afa9e1eb99bf13e945e8f4b8aced.poster.avif?t=1756929724\" width=616 height=331 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177010/extras/15d6afa9e1eb99bf13e945e8f4b8aced.webm?t=1756929724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了城市的喧嚣，主角前往乡间小屋放松心情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好为一个看似微不足道的错误承担严重后果吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索河流与大坝背后的秘密……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >款带有额外机制的步行模拟器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >河钓</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与海狸捉迷藏和追逐的机制</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177010/extras/c68152f881b99c0decf7773bc9262dac.poster.avif?t=1756929724\" width=616 height=331 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177010/extras/c68152f881b99c0decf7773bc9262dac.webm?t=1756929724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美的画面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只海狸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中享受一场“户外散步”</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏时长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30–60 分钟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机器翻译</p>",
